title: TUESDAY 1/19 - Patrick Mahomes' health update 2021
itunes:title: TUESDAY 1/19 - Patrick Mahomes' health update 2021
description:
Will Patrick Mahomes be available for the AFC title game? We have a status update (0:08) on his health. Meanwhile, on the NFC side (0:47), The Buccaneers and Packers be playing in frigid conditions in Green Bay, but Bruce Arians doesn't seemed too concerned about it (1:09). We have the latest on coaching interviews and hirings (1:33) as well as unrest in Los Angeles (2:53) as Jared Goff and Sean McVay's relationship hitting a rough patch.
